value: Coasts and islands of s South America and Falkland Islands

Breeds on both coasts of southern South America from the Province of Arauco, Chile, and Patagonian coast of Argentina, south to Tierra del Fuego; Falkland, South Shetland and South Orkney Islands. Winters north to Chimbote Bay, Peru, and to coasts of Bahia, Brazil.
